1
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,599
I told Liu Gonggong before

2
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:45,439
that consuming the Thorn Flower in the yard with fish

3
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,920
can produce a deadly poison.

4
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,599
That statement was true.

5
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,680
So,

6
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,519
whoever carries the scent of the Thorn Flower

7
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,319
is the most suspicious.

8
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,480
The day I first arrived at the Manor,

9
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,680
as soon as I entered the main hall,

10
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:05,439
I noticed that scent.

11
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,599
On the day Huang Cui died,

12
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,199
around her body,

13
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,680
I also smelled the Thorn Flower.

14
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:15,960
Siniang,

15
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,319
I suspect you got pollen on your fingertips,

16
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,439
then fed Huang Cui a fish cake,

17
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,199
and right under Liu Gonggong's nose,

18
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,879
you poisoned her.

19
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:30,879
I thought you did it to avenge the Manor Lord,

20
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,439
and that is why you killed Huang Cui.

21
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,240
I was once convinced of that answer.

22
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,520
But that day,

23
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,919
when I led Xiao Bai into the cave,

24
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,680
on the hairpin she was wearing,

25
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,240
I smelled that same scent.

26
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,199
Don't be afraid.

27
00:02:53,479 --> 00:02:55,000
So there is more than one killer.

28
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,599
Pollen isn't easy to carry around.

29
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,360
Putting it in a pouch

30
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,360
would arouse suspicion.

31
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,120
I suspect you hid the pollen

32
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,520
in the grooves of your hairpins

33
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,039
and passed it around that way.

34
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:32,240
If that's the case,

35
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,759
then tell me,

36
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:38,520
why did she want to kill Huang Cui?

37
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,840
The reason for killing

38
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:58,159
I want you to tell me yourself

39
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,039
Zhao Yun

40
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:06,680
Zhao Heng, Censor of Zhongzhou, committed treason for personal gain

41
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,000
We are here to confiscate the house by imperial decree

42
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,520
That day, ten years ago

43
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:12,840
Father never returned after going to court

44
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,120
That night

45
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,600
A group of people in white masks rushed into my home

46
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,800
Young Lady, come with me, quickly

47
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:21,560
The Manor Lord said

48
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,879
Slaughter the entire Zhao household

49
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,480
Nine Thousand Years offers a reward

50
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,639
Yes

51
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,680
The Zhao family

52
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,399
Was destroyed just like that at the hands of All-Knowing Manor

53
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:39,120
You are my only relative left in this world

54
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,839
So I cannot drag you down with me

55
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,959
So I left without saying goodbye

56
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,959
So you left on your own

57
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,000
I thought you...

58
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,199
The people who broke into my home wore masks

59
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,839
After I left

60
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:04,600
I kept looking for people wearing the same masks

61
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,000
Perseverance pays off

62
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,600
I finally found them

63
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,759
You lay low in the manor for so many years

64
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:14,519
If you wanted revenge

65
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,600
You had countless opportunities

66
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,680
Why did you hide until now?

67
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,879
Why?

68
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,720
My father was upright all his life

69
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,720
I cannot let him bear the unjust charges

70
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:29,879
of colluding with the enemy, treason, and rebellion.

71
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,800
I cannot let my mother

72
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,639
My younger brother

73
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,879
And the 103 people of my Zhao household die in vain

74
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,480
I had to find the truth

75
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,600
And clear the Zhao family's name

76
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,879
Nine Thousand Years colluded with Mo Country

77
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:49,160
Sold the Map of Frontier Iron Mines

78
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,360
My father discovered this

79
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,759
So he framed my father

80
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:00,879
All-Knowing Manor aided the tyrant

81
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:02,000
And killed my whole family

82
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,040
Taking the Manor Lord's life is easy

83
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,639
But to make all

84
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:10,839
The murderers who harmed my family face justice

85
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,920
Is not something that happens overnight

86
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,839
Nine Thousand Years has been in the court

87
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:19,879
Operating for many years

88
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:21,720
And wields absolute power

89
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,240
If I wanted revenge

90
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,959
I had to wait

91
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,120
Wait for an opportunity

92
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,560
Have you seen this child?

93
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,399
No, I haven't

94
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,079
Have you seen him?

95
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:38,079
Go ask someone else

96
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,160
I have seen this child

97
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:49,839
Where is he?

98
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:51,319
Where is my brother?

99
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:52,879
All-Knowing Manor

100
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,519
Take me there

101
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,120
I'm going right now

102
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:01,399
Outsiders cannot enter the manor

103
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:03,360
You need an identity

104
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:05,639
Use your head

105
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,720
Huang Cui listened to me

106
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,680
And successfully entered the manor to work

107
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,879
Because Young Lady Xu Qingqing was simple-minded since childhood

108
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,839
And was locked in the courtyard by the Manor Lord, seeing no guests

109
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:44,000
Huang Cui became the only one who got along with her

110
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,279
Which caught the Manor Lord's attention

111
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,519
I also fanned the flames from the sidelines

112
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,079
Saying she and the Young Lady looked more like sisters

113
00:08:02,879 --> 00:08:04,480
So the Manor Lord felt at ease keeping her

114
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,680
I didn't expect

115
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:34,240
That Huang Cui could gain the Manor Lord's trust so quickly

116
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:36,159
In less than two years

117
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,240
She became the manor's housekeeper

118
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:41,679
Later, she started pretending to be the Manor Lord's daughter

119
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:46,120
Perhaps the blood feud of a murdered loved one

120
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:48,759
Really can make a person capable of anything

121
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:52,519
Housekeeper Huang

122
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,759
Can we speak in private?

123
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,080
What is the matter, Miss Xiao Bai?

124
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,919
Housekeeper Huang is highly valued by the Manor Lord these days

125
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:13,519
Can we continue our marketplace acquaintance?

126
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:15,200
You are...

127
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,600
Thank you for your guidance, Miss Xiao Bai

128
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,759
Get up, quickly

129
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:43,559
There is something I must tell you truthfully.

130
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:49,039
After we parted ways in the market that day,

131
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,519
I returned to the Manor

132
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:52,919
and asked around for news of Yu'er everywhere.

133
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:55,679
But I was isolated and helpless in the Manor,

134
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,480
unable to make a single move.

135
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:02,200
In the end,

136
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:05,799
when I finally found news of Yu'er,

137
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,600
he was already gone.

138
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:23,960
I told Huang Cui how Ding Da kidnapped Yu'er to the Manor

139
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,159
to die in place of Master Liu's son,

140
00:10:26,919 --> 00:10:28,600
revealing every detail to her.

141
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:31,440
hoping she would lend me a hand.

142
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:37,039
All-Knowing Manor and Nine Thousand Years behind it

143
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,960
treat human life like dirt,

144
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,919
killing the innocent indiscriminately.

145
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,799
As long as these evildoers are not eliminated,

146
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:47,759
there will be more children like Yu'er

147
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,200
who die innocent and in vain.

148
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,639
Do you want to avenge your brother?

149
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,759
I do.

150
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:10,039
You look so much like the Young Lady.
